1. node js (express js frame work) => backend
2. react js => frontend 
3. mongoose (mongo db) => database

# Umuahia South Youth Platform

A comprehensive web platform for youth registration, information dissemination, and community engagement in Umuahia South LGA, Abia State, Nigeria.

![Umuahia South Youth Platform](https://via.placeholder.com/1200x600/3B82F6/ffffff?text=Umuahia+South+Youth+Platform)

